  "lore": {
    "key": "Tbl_Unit_Desc_158",
    "english": "Among the humans who have immigrated to the Demon Realm, they have taken the place of officers in an evil demonic cult. They act as \"executioners\" who track down and execute heretics who defy the cult, or try to run away from it. They are ruthless with their crossbow, hunting down their prey.",
